t":1},{"word":"places","count":1},{"word":"tuners","count":1},{"word":"however","count":1},{"word":"memories","count":1},{"word":"tend","count":1},{"word":"play","count":1},{"word":"tricks","count":1},{"word":"age","count":1},{"word":"eyes","count":1},{"word":"certain","count":1},{"word":"relying","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"objectives","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"dwelling","count":1},{"word":"melancholy","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"gets","count":1},{"word":"stronger","count":1},{"word":"content","count":1},{"word":"cry","count":1},{"word":"grandpa","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"yingying","count":1},{"word":"grandma","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"carefully","count":1},{"word":"consider","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"purpose","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"bring","count":1},{"word":"safely","count":1},{"word":"reassuring","count":1},{"word":"support","count":1},{"word":"comes","count":1},{"word":"safety","count":1},{"word":"helpers","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"inadequate","count":1},{"word":"express","count":1},{"word":"gratitude","count":1},{"word":"gone","count":1},{"word":"cave","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"edge","count":1},{"word":"easy","count":1},{"word":"clue","count":1},{"word":"mention","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"jogged","count":1},{"word":"serves","count":1},{"word":"gathering","count":1},{"word":"flautist","count":1},{"word":"given","count":1},{"word":"health","count":1},{"word":"venture","count":1},{"word":"exploring","count":1},{"word":"scattered","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"relied","count":1},{"word":"experience","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"advanced","count":1},{"word":"technologies","count":1},{"word":"available","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hey there, it’s Jingzhu! I’m reaching out once again to ask for the help of you young folks.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"As usual, I’m doing just fine!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"A valiant Midnight Ranger like myself won’t be deterred by a few setbacks!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Since we last met, I’ve been pondering a more practical approach...","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"And I’ve finally devised one! Eager to put it into action!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Hehe, yes. I’ve thought it over and I do need the help of you young folks.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"You don’t sound very enthusiastic, but it doesn’t matter. Once you arrive, you’ll be immediately convinced that my plan will work this time!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"I’ll be waiting for you at the Jinzhou Theater, and that red-haired Patroller will be joining us as well.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"And don’t you worry, I’ve already prepared your payment. I won’t let you work for free.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Alright then, see you later!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Alright then, see you later!","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"My captain taught me a lot... from uncovering Tacet Fields to identifying various Tacet Discords, even the places to find Tuners...","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"However, memories tend to play tricks as you age, so I must see it with my own eyes to be certain.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Even in the wild, I find myself relying on you young ones to help me reach my objectives.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"But enough dwelling on the melancholy. As long as the Echo gets stronger, I’m content.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"No, no, no, don’t cry. Tell Grandpa what happened.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Don’t worry, Yingying. Grandma will be alright. She’ll be back home soon.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"I must carefully consider why Linghan went out today. There must be a purpose behind it.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Ah, I see... Today is... I know where she is. No need to worry. I’ll bring her back home safely.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"It’s reassuring to have your support. When it comes to Linghan’s safety, the more helpers, the better.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Thank you, young ones... Words are inadequate to express my gratitude.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"I think she might have gone to that cave near the edge of Jinzhou.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Easy there, young one. There’s a clue that could help us locate Linghan swiftly.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"Now that you mention it, something just jogged my memory. It might help us locate Linghan swiftly.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"If my memory serves me right, she should be gathering the Echo of Flautist. Given her health, she wouldn’t venture to Tacet Fields, so she must be exploring the wild for scattered Tacet Discords.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021},{"text":"In our day, we relied on experience to locate Tacet Discords, but I’ve heard there are more advanced technologies available now.","quest_name":"Silver-haired Echo Trainer - III","quest_id":139000021}]}